Most Recent News 
 
Major Structural Change to the Equinox Chesapeake Strategy Fund
July 26, 2017 – Shareholders have approved a new fee structure in which Chesapeake Capital will be a sub-advisor to the Fund, managing a portion of the Fund’s assets more directly, and not be paid any additional advisory fee or performance-based incentive fee. 



 
‘Best Multi-Manager Fund’
The Equinox MutualHedge Futures Strategy Fund is named the Best Multi-Manager Fund award at the 2017 CTA US Performance Awards.



 
